'''Janx Ferro''' was a [[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorian]] [[Commander/Legends|Commander]] and hero who was given control of the Mandalorian forces protecting [[Governor/Legends|Governor]] [[Vrox]] at the [[Battle of Mandalore (pre-Naboo)|Battle of Mandalore]]. It was thought that he was killed in the battle before Vrox was captured.<ref name="BFM">{{ChallengeCite|58|Battle for Mandalore}}</ref>

